governance decisions need context.

Example:
{
  "command": "approve_trade",
  "actor": "operator",
  "amount": 1200000
}
Without state, the system cannot know:
	•	risk level
	•	domain condition
	•	authority escalation requirement

So we introduce:
SYSTEM_STATE
DOMAIN_STATE
AUTHORITY_STATE
The system state includes:
    •	risk level
    • domain condition
    • authority escalation requirement